ions/home-office","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_roles":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/minister-for-security-and-immigration","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/minister-for-security-and-immigration","base_path":"/government/ministers/minister-for-security-and-immigration","content_id":"84707c1c-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The minister is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>immigration and border policy (including non-EU migration to the UK; family reunion; border security; detention and removal policy; asylum policy; post-Brexit immigration policy for EU nationals)</li>\n  <li>assisting Secretary of State with all policy on exiting the European Union</li>\n  <li>international policy, including EU Justice and Home Affairs</li>\n  <li>border security</li>\n  <li>foreign national offenders (management in immigration detention and deportation to country of origin)</li>\n  <li>resettlement policy (including the operation of Home Office resettlement programmes: Syrian Vulnerable Persons Resettlement Scheme; Gateway; Mandate; and Vulnerable Children’s Resettlement Scheme)</li>\n  <li>implementation of the Immigration Act 2016</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration\">UK Visas and Immigration</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/immigration-enforcement\">Immigration Enforcement</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/border-force\">Border Force</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/hm-passport-office\">His Majesty’s Passport Office</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://icinspector.independent.gov.uk/\">Independent Chief Inspector of Borders and Immigration</a></li>\n  <li>Home Office immigration transparency data</li>\n  <li>net migration statistics</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":15,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministe